OL,3,CRow over proposed 8.5% council tax
OL,4,Crise in Scottish Borders
OL,6,FSNP councillors have challenged the
OL,7,Fcouncil tax rise put forward by
OL,8,FConservative leader of Scottish
OL,9,FBorders Council Euan Jardine.
OL,11,FIn previous years all parties
OL,12,F(Conservative, SNP, Lib-Dem and
OL,13,FIndependents) have agreed on finalised
OL,14,Fproposals before they are publicly
OL,15,Freleased.
OL,17,FBut this week the draft budget fell
OL,18,Fafoul of part politics and the SNP
OL,19,Fwalked out of discussions at the 11th
OL,20,Fhour.
