OL,6,FWaste services would also remain
OL,7,Funchanged - compared to some other
OL,8,Fcouncils in Scotland who have moved to
OL,9,Fthree-week collection cycles.
OL,11,FThe draft budget was supported by a
OL,12,Fcross-party working group including
OL,13,Fthe conservatives, liberal democrats,
OL,14,Findependents, SNP and green
OL,15,Fcouncillors up until Tuesday 10
OL,16,FFebruary when collaboration broke down
OL,17,Fand the SNP and Greens councillor
OL,18,Fwalked out.
