OL,4,Crise in Scottish Borders
OL,6,F"Ordinary people across the Scottish
OL,7,FBorders are doing everything they can
OL,8,Fto balance their own budgets," said
OL,9,FCouncillor Elaine Thornton-Nicol,
OL,10,FLeader of the Opposition.
OL,12,F"It is simply not right that they are
OL,13,Fbeing asked to shoulder an 8.5% rise
OL,14,Fwhile a phased and gentler approach is
OL,15,Fbeing taken on other measures.
