OL,4,Crise in Scottish Borders
OL,6,FAn 8.5% increase in council tax for
OL,7,FBand D properties equates to #2.44 per
OL,8,Fweek, or an extra #126.88 per year.
OL,10,F"The people of the Borders are at the
OL,11,Fheart of this budget, we are
OL,12,Fprotecting services that they have
OL,13,Ftold us they hold dear and that we
OL,14,Fknow have an impact on everyday
OL,15,Flives," said Councillor Euan Jardine,
OL,16,FLeader of Scottish Borders Council.
