OL,4,Crise in Scottish Borders
OL,6,F"As a council, we are asked year on
OL,7,Fyear to deliver more with fewer
OL,8,Fresources, we will continue to make
OL,9,Fclear the significant pressures this
OL,10,Fplaces on essential services in our
OL,11,Flocal area.
OL,13,FDespite ongoing pressures on our
OL,14,Ffunding, we have made decisions to
OL,15,Fmaintain services."
