OL,3,CRow over proposed 8.5% council tax
OL,4,Crise in Scottish Borders
OL,6,FScottish Borders Council recognises
OL,7,Fthat, across Scotland, local
OL,8,Fauthorities are facing increasing
OL,9,Fdemands driving financial pressure,
OL,10,Fand the situation highlighted by COSLA
OL,11,Freflects the very real strain this is
OL,12,Fplacing on essential local services.
OL,14,FCouncillor Robin Tatler, leader of the
OL,15,FIndependent group, said: "Once again
OL,16,Fwe have had to make considerable
OL,17,Fsavings in order to submit a balanced
OL,18,Fbudget, whilst continuing to protect
OL,19,Ffrontline services.
