OL,3,CRow over proposed 8.5% council tax
OL,4,Crise in Scottish Borders
OL,6,F"Our staff must be congratulated for
OL,7,Fimplementing new technology and
OL,8,Fsystems that will make service
OL,9,Fdelivery not only more efficient but
OL,10,Fmore cost effective in the coming
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,F"The budget will also enable us to
OL,14,Fmaintain and develop local public
OL,15,Ftransport services - vital for our
OL,16,Frural communities. It is encouraging
OL,17,Fthat we have again been able to work
OL,18,Facross all groups on the council to
OL,19,Fdevelop this budget."
